lass=\"rmLink\" href=\"CountyUtilities/ManageJurisdictions.aspx\"><span class=\"rmText\">Manage Jurisdictions</span></a></li><li class=\"rmItem \"><a class=\"rmLink\" href=\"CountyUtilities/JurisdictionSplits.aspx\"><span class=\"rmText\">Splits in Jurisdictions</span></a></li><li class=\"rmItem \"><a class=\"rmLink\" href=\"VR/AbsenteeBatch.aspx\"><span class=\"rmText\">Process Batch Absentees</span></a></li><li class=\"rmItem \"><a class=\"rmLink\" href=\"CountyUtilities/AbsenteeEmail.aspx\"><span class=\"rmText\">Absentee Emails</span></a></li><li class=\"rmItem \"><a class=\"rmLink\" href=\"CountyUtilities/PollbookManagement.aspx\"><span class=\"rmText\">Pollbook Management</span></a></li><li class=\"rmItem \"><a class=\"rmLink\" href=\"VR/PossibleDuplicates.aspx\"><span class=\"rmText\">Possible Duplicates</span></a></li><li class=\"rmItem \"><a class=\"rmLink\" href=\"CountyUtilities/MergeVoters.aspx\"><span class=\"rmText\">Merge Voters</span></a></li><li class=\"rmItem \"><a class=\"rmLink\" href=\"CountyUtilities/PurgeList.aspx\"><span class=\"rmText\">List Maintenance</span></a></li><li class=\"rmItem \"><a class=\"rmLink\" href=\"CountyUtilities/PurgeListReturns.aspx\"><span class=\"rmText\">List Maintenance Returns</span></a></li><li class=\"rmItem \"><a class=\"rmLink\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"VR/DeathSearch.aspx\"><span class=\"rmText\">Death Records Search</span></a></li><li class=\"rmItem \"><a class=\"rmLink\" href=\"CountyUtilities/HistoryExport.aspx\"><span class=\"rmText\">Voter History Export</span></a></li><li class=\"rmItem \"><a class=\"rmLink\" href=\"CountyUtilities/VoterCounts.aspx\"><span class=\"rmText\">Voter Counts</span></a></li><li class=\"rmItem \"><a class=\"rmLink\" href=\"StateUtilities/StateEmails.aspx\"><span class=\"rmText\">State Emails</span></a></li><li class=\"rmItem rmSeparator\"><span class=\"rmText\"></span></li><li class=\"rmItem rmLast\"><a class=\"rmLink\" href=\"#\"><span class=\"rmText\">User Manuals</span></a></li>\r\n\t\t\t</ul>\r\n\t\t</div></li>\r\n\t</ul><input id=\"ctl00_rmMaster_ClientState\" name=\"ctl00_rmMaster_ClientState\" type=\"hidden\" />\r\n</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mastersearch\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"pnlSearch\" onkeypress=\"javascript:return WebForm_FireDefaultButton(event, &#39;btnGo&#39;)\">\r\n\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<table align=\"right\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr style=\"padding-top: 5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"3\">Quick Search</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"margin-left: 40px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<input name=\"ctl00$txtLast\" type=\"text\" id=\"txtLast\" class=\"textentry\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<input name=\"ctl00$txtFirst\" type=\"text\" id=\"txtFirst\" class=\"textentry\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<input name=\"ctl00$txtVoterID\" type=\"text\" id=\"txtVoterID\" class=\"textentry\" style=\"width:75px;\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"3\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<input type=\"submit\" name=\"ctl00$btnGo\" value=\"Go\" id=\"btnGo\" class=\"button\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"textboxcaption\">Last Name</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"textboxcaption\">First Name</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"textboxcaption\">Bar Code/Voter ID</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"main\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\r\n    <h2>Log In\r\n    </h2>\r\n    <p>\r\n        Please enter your username and password and then touch your e-token.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <div onkeypress=\"javascript:return WebForm_FireDefaultButton(event, &#39;MainContent_LoginUser_LoginButton&#39;)\">\r\n\t\r\n        \r\n                <span class=\"failureNotification\">\r\n                    \r\n                </span>\r\n                <div data-val-validationGroup=\"LoginUserValidationGroup\" id=\"MainContent_LoginUser_LoginUserValidationSummary\" class=\"failureNotification\" data-valsummary=\"true\" style=\"display:none;\">\r\n\r\n\t</div>\r\n                <div class=\"accountInfo\">\r\n                    <fieldset class=\"login\">\r\n                        <legend>Account Information</legend>\r\n                        <p>\r\n                            <label for=\"MainContent_LoginUser_UserName\" id=\"MainContent_LoginUser_UserNameLabel\">Username:</label>\r\n                            <input name=\"ctl00$MainContent$LoginUser$UserName\" type=\"text\" id=\"MainContent_LoginUser_UserName\" class=\"textEntry\" />\r\n                            <span data-val-controltovalidate=\"MainContent_LoginUser_UserName\" data-val-errormessage=\"User Name is required.\" data-val-validationGroup=\"LoginUserValidationGroup\" id=\"MainContent_LoginUser_UserNameRequired\" title=\"User Name is required.\" class=\"failureNotification\" data-val=\"true\" data-val-evaluationfunction=\"RequiredFieldValidatorEvaluateIsValid\" data-val-initialvalue=\"\" style=\"visibility:hidden;\">*</span>\r\n                        </p>\r\n                        <p>\r\n                            <label for=\"MainContent_LoginUser_Password\" id=\"MainContent_LoginUser_PasswordLabel\">Password:</label>\r\n                            <input name=\"ctl00$MainContent$LoginUser$Password\" type=\"password\" id=\"MainContent_LoginUser_Password\" class=\"passwordEntry\" />\r\n                            <span data-val-controltovalidate=\"MainContent_LoginUser_Password\" data-val-errormessage=\"Password is required.\" data-val-validationGroup=\"LoginUserValidationGroup\" id=\"MainContent_LoginUser_PasswordRequired\" title=\"Password is required.\" class=\"failureNotification\" data-val=\"true\" data-val-eva